{"image_id": "EXPE_2010_page_88", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "In 2009, we acquired an additional interest in an equity method investment for $3 million in cash, which", "bbox": [185.5, 140.4, 1057.1, 161.2]}, {"text": "was included within the 2009 total purchase price above, and resulted in a 60% majority ownership interest and", "bbox": [143.8, 165.4, 1075.0, 186.2]}, {"text": "our consolidation of this entity. In conjunction with our acquisition of additional interest, we remeasured our", "bbox": [143.8, 190.4, 1051.5, 211.3]}, {"text": "previously held equity interest to fair value and recognized a loss of $5 million in other, net during the period.", "bbox": [143.8, 215.4, 1061.9, 236.3]}, {"text": "The fair value of the 40% noncontrolling interest in the company was estimated to be $15 million at the time of", "bbox": [143.8, 240.4, 1074.1, 261.3]}, {"text": "acquisition. Both fair value assessments were determined based on various valuation techniques, including", "bbox": [143.8, 265.4, 1034.4, 286.3]}, {"text": "market comparables and discounted cash flow projections.", "bbox": [143.8, 290.4, 632.4, 311.3]}, {"text": "In addition to and including the 60% majority ownership interest discussed above, certain of our", "bbox": [185.5, 328.0, 989.8, 348.8]}, {"text": "acquisitions made during 2009 and 2008 include noncontrolling interests with certain rights, whereby we may", "bbox": [143.8, 353.0, 1062.8, 373.8]}, {"text": "acquire and the minority shareholders may sell to us the additional shares of the company, at fair value or at", "bbox": [143.8, 378.0, 1045.2, 398.8]}, {"text": "adjusted fair values at our discretion, during various periods from 2011 through 2013. Changes in fair value of", "bbox": [143.8, 403.0, 1066.3, 423.8]}, {"text": "the shares for which the minority holders may sell to us are recorded to the noncontrolling interest, classified in", "bbox": [143.8, 428.0, 1074.9, 448.8]}, {"text": "other long-term liabilities, and as 